<table summary="" width="366" border="0" cellspacing="0" cellpadding="0">
                  <tr>
                    <td width="366" align="left" valign="top"><p>The  entrepreneurial culture at Bank of America creates significant opportunities to  gain hands-on experience and early access to senior management.&nbsp; Our associates receive meaningful  responsibilities, active mentoring and valuable exposure to high-profile  clients and deals.&nbsp; In addition, we work  in a collaborative environment based on solid core values and an emphasis on  diversity and inclusiveness.&nbsp; </p>
                      <p>As a fast growing  organization, our Asian associates comprise talent from leading financial  services firms and universities. Why do we believe Bank of America is the best  place to build our careers? Through our shared culture and values, we each  benefit from: </p>
                      <ul>
                        <li><span class="text_bold">An inclusive and supportive workplace:</span> We respect and value the diversity of  backgrounds, experiences and perspectives of our associates and believe it is a  significant competitive advantage in serving clients and shareholders  worldwide. Diversity is more than the right thing to do, it is how we work and  win together.
                        </li>
                        <li><span class="text_bold">Career and performance development</span>: Helping associates grow professionally is an  important part of growing our success as a company. Bank of America rewards  associates based on performance and strives to help associates succeed with an  array of innovative and competitive learning and leadership programs. </li>
                      
                      <li><span class="text_bold">Cross-platform partnership</span>:  More than any one capability or area of expertise, it&rsquo;s the unique combination  of resources and talents throughout our global company that sets Bank of  America apart. We partner within and across lines of business and share a  collective responsibility for exceeding our clients&rsquo; expectations every  day.&nbsp; Integrated delivery is part of  every business plan and reflected in how we serve clients wherever they do  business.</li></ul>
  
                  </tr>
